et 809). The other, Hasan Husnu Pasha 82, 75-81, has not yet been checked.  Further work needed.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL></ROW><ROW MODID="17" RECORDID="609"><COL><DATA>135.3</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>818</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>609</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Chapter 560 of Futūḥāt</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>الباب الستون وخمسمائة من الفتوحات</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Additional category</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Chapter 560 of FM, often copied as a separate work.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>This RG has been created to list copies of Chapter 560 of FM, which was often copied as a separate work. See also RG 818.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL></ROW><ROW MODID="25" RECORDID="610"><COL><DATA>348</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>135</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>610</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>R. fī kayfiyyat aḥwāl rijāl Allāh</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>رسالة في كيفية أحوال رجال الله</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Extract.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Classification of the different kinds of saints, listing the quṭb, imāms, awtād etc.  An extract from Chapter 73 of FM.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>OY cites three mss.,  but our inspection shows that they are all extracts from Volume 2 of FM, on the people of God. </DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL></ROW><ROW MODID="31" RECORDID="611"><COL><DATA>566</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA>611</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>al-Qaṣīda al-tāʾiyya</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>القصيدة التائية</DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Not IA.</DATA></COL><COL><DATA></DATA></COL><COL><DATA>Muhammad al-Wafāʾ (d